org.forgerock.openam.radius.common.packet

Class FramedCompressionAttribute

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.forgerock.openam.radius.common.Attribute
      • org.forgerock.openam.radius.common.packet.FramedCompressionAttribute

  • public class FramedCompressionAttribute
extends Attribute
    Class representing the structure of the Framed-Compression attribute as specified in section 5.13 of RFC 2865.
